00:07.850 --> 00:10.300
My name is Melinda Gordon.

00:12.000 --> 00:13.100
I just got married,

00:13.150 --> 00:14.600
just moved to a small town,

00:14.750 --> 00:16.600
just opened up an antique shop.

00:16.850 --> 00:18.630
I might be just like you.

00:19.650 --> 00:21.550
Except from the time that I was a little girl,

00:21.600 --> 00:23.500
I knew that I could talk to the dead.

00:24.900 --> 00:26.000
It's all right,honey.

00:26.050 --> 00:28.500
Earthbound spirits,my grandmother called them,

00:28.600 --> 00:30.000
the ones who have not crossed over yet

00:30.050 --> 00:32.100
because they have unfinished business with the living,

00:32.150 --> 00:33.850
and they come to me for help.

00:35.050 --> 00:36.500
To tell you my story,

00:36.700 --> 00:38.550
I have to tell you theirs.

